headline: New Ownership of 36-Year-Old AIM Mail Center in Rancho Santa Margarita, CA Set to Offer Extended Hours and Expanded Office Services
summary: Annex Brands, Inc., a leading franchisor in the packing, shipping, and office services industries, is pleased to announce the successful transfer of ownership of an existing AIM Mail Center location in Rancho Santa Margarita, CA to new owner, Venus Qurbanzadeh. This transition to new ownership ensures that the community will continue to benefit from the essential shipping and office services provided by this AIM Mail Center for the last 36 years.
